			<h1 id="firstHeading" class="firstHeading" lang="en"><span dir="auto">Using Weightmaps to texture a Landscape</span></h1>
			<div id="bodyContent">
				<div id="contentSub"><div id="mw-revision-info">Revision as of 18:08, 2 October 2014 by <a href="/index.php?title=User:Neighborlee&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new mw-userlink" title="User:Neighborlee (page does not exist)">Neighborlee</a>  <span class="mw-usertoollinks">(<a href="/index.php?title=User_talk:Neighborlee&amp;action=edit&amp;redlink=1" class="new" title="User talk:Neighborlee (page does not exist)">Talk</a> | <a href="/Special:Contributions/Neighborlee" title="Special:Contributions/Neighborlee">contribs</a>)</span></div><br />
